&lt;li&gt;3–5+ years managing multi-function operational teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep understanding of cash application, invoicing, and billing support processes in a SaaS, hardware, or subscription business.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong analytical mindset with experience owning operational KPIs and reporting.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven ability to lead change, streamline processes, and implement scalable systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication skills and stakeholder management experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with NetSuite and ticketing systems (Zendesk, Salesforce Service Cloud).&lt;/li&gt;
